Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,35... 36... {\alpha&HFF&}37... 38... 39...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.87,0:00:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,35... 36... 37... {\alpha&HFF&}38... 39...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.42,0:00:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,35... 36... 37... 38... {\alpha&HFF&}39...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.18,0:00:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,35... 36... 37... 38... 39...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, {\alpha&HFF&}it's my victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.84,0:00:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, it's my victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,40!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:36.26,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs72\pos(366,365)}New World
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.64,0:00:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't die...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.25,0:01:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One minute has passed... {\alpha&HFF&}and we didn't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.95,0:01:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One minute has passed... and we didn't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.37,0:01:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I told you several times we wouldn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.03,0:01:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't they die!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.37,0:01:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-{\alpha&HFF&}God! I did everything you told me to!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.84,0:01:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-God! {\alpha&HFF&}I did everything you told me to!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.90,0:01:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-God! I did everything you told me to!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.39,0:01:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lester, Gevanni, seize Mikami!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gevanni, the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.38,0:01:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please confirm this with your own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.85,0:01:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first four are, without a doubt, the SPK members' real names.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the only one here whose name isn't written down, is... {\alpha&HFF&}Yagami Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the only one here whose name isn't written down, is... Yagami Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.80,0:01:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikami also called you "God", and said he did as you instructed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:01:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.05,0:02:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap!! {\alpha&HFF&}This is a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.61,0:02:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap!! This is a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a trap set by Near in order to frame me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.31,0:02:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Writing the names in the notebook and not dying, isn't that strange?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That proves it's a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.56,0:02:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you that I modified the notebook so that we wouldn't die?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.32,0:02:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-{\alpha&HFF&}Not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.80,0:02:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.92,0:02:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.65,0:02:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a trap... {\alpha&HFF&}I don't even know that person!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.89,0:02:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a trap... I don't even know that person!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun, {\alpha&HFF&}it's too late... Near won.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.56,0:02:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun, it's too late... {\alpha&HFF&}Near won.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun, it's too late... Near won.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.59,0:02:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you just said, "It's my victory".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the same as a confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.93,0:03:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-{\alpha&HFF&}Stop!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.51,0:03:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.44,0:03:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light, {\alpha&HFF&}"L", Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light, "L", {\alpha&HFF&}Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.52,0:03:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light, "L", Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.92,0:03:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.74,0:03:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just now, you proclaimed your victory...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.97,0:03:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although originally you would have won, {\alpha&HFF&}and I would have lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.92,0:03:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although originally you would have won, and I would have lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.56,0:03:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All this time we did exactly as you predicted, {\alpha&HFF&}and altered the fake notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All this time we did exactly as you predicted, and altered the fake notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Except, earlier, when I said that I modified the notebook, {\alpha&HFF&}that applied to the real notebook as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.85,0:03:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Except, earlier, when I said that I modified the notebook, that applied to the real notebook as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.19,0:03:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fake one was only slightly modified...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real one was replaced entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the real notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.19,0:04:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Im-{\alpha&HFF&}Impossible!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.12,0:04:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Im-Impossible!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.42,0:04:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the same pen that Mikami used, {\alpha&HFF&}in the same handwriting...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the same pen that Mikami used, in the same handwriting...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.51,0:04:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything looks identical.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.09,0:04:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gevanni made this for us in one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.43,0:04:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I touched this notebook, I have been able to see the Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.49,0:04:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami-san, a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.53,0:04:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.12,0:04:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.62,0:04:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's having a conversation with Ryuk...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.25,0:04:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being able to see him must mean it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.69,0:04:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this notebook, it seems that a number of pages have been ripped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.48,0:04:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone's name is written on a torn page, would they die?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they'd die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.03,0:04:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So there are a number of ways to use it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder just how many people you killed, and how many times we've been fooled...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.42,0:05:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something wrong here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.41,0:05:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that Mikami betrayed me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all thanks to Mello.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.89,0:05:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saying this much, you should understand by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.15,0:05:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take a good look at this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada's name is in the notebook!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who killed Takada, {\alpha&HFF&}and that one is set for one minute later!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who killed Takada, and that one is set for one minute later!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, did Mikami also...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God, you said you were being watched and couldn't act!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.59,0:05:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Takada in that situation... it was my duty to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.39,0:05:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You IDIOT!! I told you NOT to do anything unnecessary until today!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.59,0:05:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the 26th, {\alpha&HFF&}after the report featuring Takada's kidnapping, Mikami headed for the bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.31,0:06:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the 26th, after the report featuring Takada's kidnapping, Mikami headed for the bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to my investigation, {\alpha&HFF&}Mikami only goes to the bank on the 25th of every month.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to my investigation, Mikami only goes to the bank on the 25th of every month.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.98,0:06:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For someone as punctual as Mikami, going to the bank twice in two days is pretty unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I followed him as he headed for the deposit boxes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.83,0:06:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And only at that moment did he appear to be afraid of being tailed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to get into the deposit box, {\alpha&HFF&}and inside, was the real notebook, with Takada's name written in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to get into the deposit box, and inside, {\alpha&HFF&}was the real notebook, with Takada's name written in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.35,0:06:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to get into the deposit box, and inside, was the real notebook, {\alpha&HFF&}with Takada's name written in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.17,0:06:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to get into the deposit box, and inside, was the real notebook, with Takada's name written in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you could kill someone with a piece of the note, you weren't aware that Mikami had done something on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.86,0:06:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was then that I realized the possibility of a fake notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.69,0:06:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The biggest help in creating this scenario... {\alpha&HFF&}was Mello.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.53,0:06:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The biggest help in creating this scenario... was Mello.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.65,0:07:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello might have known this would happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By directly writing down your names in the notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.33,0:07:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one who can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.44,0:07:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello knew this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.69,0:07:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alone, neither Mello nor I could surpass L...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But together... {\alpha&HFF&}together, we are as able as L.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But together... together, we are as able as L.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Together, we can surpass L!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.37,0:07:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now as one... {\alpha&HFF&}against Kira who L himself couldn't take down, it's us who has the evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now as one... against Kira who L himself couldn't take down, it's us who has the evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.42,0:07:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can talk your way out of this, by all means, please do...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.34,0:08:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.34,0:08:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Kira.
Comment: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EYECATCHERS
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.13,0:08:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.46,0:08:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.34,0:08:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, {\alpha&HFF&}I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also... {\alpha&HFF&}God of the new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also... God of the new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the world we live in today, Kira is the law and protecting order.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon I will be justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.14,0:09:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hope of all mankind...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the six years Kira has existed, {\alpha&HFF&}wars have ceased, violent criminals have almost died out...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.15,0:09:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the six years Kira has existed, wars have ceased, {\alpha&HFF&}violent criminals have almost died out...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the six years Kira has existed, wars have ceased, violent criminals have almost died out...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this world still rots!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.68,0:09:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are too many rotten people...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody has to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.15,0:09:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the time I obtained the notebook, {\alpha&HFF&}I realized I had to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.02,0:09:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the time I obtained the notebook, I realized I had to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... {\alpha&HFF&}Only I could do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Only I could do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that killing people was a crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:09:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there was no other way to correct things!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the purpose given to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only I could do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who else could have done it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To come this far?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.07,0:10:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be able to go on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.03,0:10:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To create a new world... {\alpha&HFF&}Only I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.57,0:10:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To create a new world... Only I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.91,0:10:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... {\alpha&HFF&}you are just a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.07,0:10:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... you are just a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this notebook is the deadliest weapon in the history of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lost yourself to the Shinigami and to the power of the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.59,0:10:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're mistaken, thinking of becoming a God. {\alpha&HFF&}You're only a crazy mass murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're mistaken, thinking of becoming a God. You're only a crazy mass murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.15,0:10:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.74,0:11:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like those fools would understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.77,0:11:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, {\alpha&HFF&}the note you're holding...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, the note you're holding...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.24,0:11:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the one that Aizawa brought from the Japanese Investigation HQ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.95,0:11:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they real?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he attempting to bluff?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one who knows if it's the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to defeat Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}and prove that Aizawa's note is real...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to defeat Kira, and prove that Aizawa's note is real...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.60,0:11:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll just have to write down mine or Mikami's name to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.87,0:12:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the note is real... {\alpha&HFF&}or a fake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the note is real... or a fake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.13,0:12:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a hidden note!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You asshole!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.31,0:12:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda! {\alpha&HFF&}Who do you think you're shooting at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.67,0:12:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda! Who do you think you're shooting at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.50,0:12:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fuck with me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.92,0:12:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father... {\alpha&HFF&}what did he die for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father... what did he die for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Yagami Souichiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Matsuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.79,0:12:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Serious people like that, crowned with justice, always lose in the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay living in such a society?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you'll understand, so kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SHOOT THEM!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You drove your own father to his death...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.62,0:13:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now you're saying they are the fools?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill... {\alpha&HFF&}I have to kill him!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill... I have to kill him!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is t-{\alpha&HFF&}this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.33,0:13:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is t-this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.08,0:13:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikami... {\alpha&HFF&}what the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikami... what the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:13:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Write!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.61,0:14:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.62,0:14:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, {\alpha&HFF&}it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.27,0:14:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.44,0:14:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, where are you??
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Takada?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.33,0:14:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-{\alpha&HFF&}Someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts... {\alpha&HFF&}What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts... What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mi-{\alpha&HFF&}Mikami is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mi-Mikami is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.30,0:14:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.71,0:15:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun! {\alpha&HFF&}Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun! Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Aizawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He shouldn't have any more hidden notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.03,0:15:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he can't get far with those wounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.36,0:15:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just leave him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, {\alpha&HFF&}I can't follow your orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.79,0:15:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, I can't follow your orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.61,0:15:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand... {\alpha&HFF&}I'll leave him to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand... I'll leave him to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.14,0:17:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have lost, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.30,0:17:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the beginning, didn't I say... {\alpha&HFF&}at the time of your death, I will be the one who'll write down your name in my notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.99,0:17:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the beginning, didn't I say... at the time of your death, {\alpha&HFF&}I will be the one who'll write down your name in my notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.96,0:17:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the beginning, didn't I say... at the time of your death, I will be the one who'll write down your name in my notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.14,0:17:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the deal made between the Shinigami and the first human to possess the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you enter a prison, there's no telling when you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's annoying to wait... {\alpha&HFF&}your life is already over...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's annoying to wait... your life is already over...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:17:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.57,0:18:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was good while it lasted...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.00,0:18:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We killed some boredom, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.08,0:18:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did various interesting things...
